Revered TV and radio personality Penny Lebyane is embroiled in a bitter legal battle with her former boyfriend Ali Naka. This after Naka refused to sign travel documents for Lebyane and her family to travel to Swaziland for their Christmas holiday. Lebyane confirmed she dragged Naka to court for refusing to sign her documents. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE